{"serial": "41023", "department_serial": 40, "code": "BA5077", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "AIoT Product Development", "ch": "AIoT產品發展實作"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liu,Shu Ming", "Chen, Shiuann-Shuoh"], "ch": ["劉書銘", "陳炫碩"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "018"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 65, "department": {"ch": "企業管理學系", "en": "Department of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 41, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "從實作中學習如何利用Design Thinking的方法，找出使用者需求，並利用Raspberry Pi 與OpenCV 開發出AIoT應用的產品原型。", "en": "從實作中學習如何利用Design Thinking的方法，找出使用者需求，並利用Raspberry Pi 與OpenCV 開發出AIoT應用的產品原型。"}, "outline": {"ch": "自從SAP的創辦人Hasso Plattner捐獻設立Stanford 大學的d. School, Design Thinking 已成為很多公司商品開發的重要方法之一,本課程是以SAP的Design Thinking Methodology 為主軸, 學生可針對某一類需求, 發展出一個可行有效的產品概念。這個方法論主要分成三階段\n第一階段: 定義問題\n透過觀察、訪問、與實際沈浸於與使用者相同的情境，了解真正需要解決的問題。\n第二階段: 創意發想\n針對上述的問題，透過腦力激盪等方法，找出解決的方法。\n第三階段: 快速模型(rapid prototyping)及測試\n將上述的方法具體化成產品原型，並取得使用者的回饋。\n在第三個階段，學生需利用嵌入式系統裝置，發展出一個產品原型，以具體化的方式收集使用者回饋，在重複下一個三階段的循環。\nSessionTopicNote\n1Course Overview\nDesign Thinking – Background ＆ Methodology\nDesign Thinking – Empathy\nTeam mobilization\nInterview\nObserving\nRecording\n2Design Thinking – Define\nIdeas for Project Point-of-viewing\nStory Telling\nEmpathy Mapping\n3Design Thinking – Ideate\nProject ProposalBrainstorming\n4Design Thinking – Prototyping\nFinalizing Project Proposal\nIntroduction to Raspberry Pi\n5Python\n6Raspberry Pi ＆ Open CV\n7Raspberry Pi ＆ API\n8Design Thinking – Prototyping\n9Design Thinking – Prototyping\n10Design Thinking – Prototyping\n11Project Review\n12Design Thinking – Testing\n13Iteration\n14Design Thinking – Prototyping ＆ Testing\n15Second Iteration – Prototyping ＆ Testing\n16Final Presentation", "en": "自從SAP的創辦人Hasso Plattner捐獻設立Stanford 大學的d. School, Design Thinking 已成為很多公司商品開發的重要方法之一,本課程是以SAP的Design Thinking Methodology 為主軸, 學生可針對某一類需求, 發展出一個可行有效的產品概念。這個方法論主要分成三階段\n第一階段: 定義問題\n透過觀察、訪問、與實際沈浸於與使用者相同的情境，了解真正需要解決的問題。\n第二階段: 創意發想\n針對上述的問題，透過腦力激盪等方法，找出解決的方法。\n第三階段: 快速模型(rapid prototyping)及測試\n將上述的方法具體化成產品原型，並取得使用者的回饋。\n在第三個階段，學生需利用嵌入式系統裝置，發展出一個產品原型，以具體化的方式收集使用者回饋，在重複下一個三階段的循環。\nSessionTopicNote\n1Course Overview\nDesign Thinking – Background ＆ Methodology\nDesign Thinking – Empathy\nTeam mobilization\nInterview\nObserving\nRecording\n2Design Thinking – Define\nIdeas for Project Point-of-viewing\nStory Telling\nEmpathy Mapping\n3Design Thinking – Ideate\nProject ProposalBrainstorming\n4Design Thinking – Prototyping\nFinalizing Project Proposal\nIntroduction to Raspberry Pi\n5Python\n6Raspberry Pi ＆ Open CV\n7Raspberry Pi ＆ API\n8Design Thinking – Prototyping\n9Design Thinking – Prototyping\n10Design Thinking – Prototyping\n11Project Review\n12Design Thinking – Testing\n13Iteration\n14Design Thinking – Prototyping ＆ Testing\n15Second Iteration – Prototyping ＆ Testing\n16Final Presentation"}, "textbook": {"ch": "AIOT與OpenCV實戰應用：Python、樹莓派、物聯網與機器視覺/ 朱克剛著 – 三版.—碁峰資訊，2021.11", "en": "AIOT與OpenCV實戰應用：Python、樹莓派、物聯網與機器視覺/ 朱克剛著 – 三版.—碁峰資訊，2021.11"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50%", "en": "50%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n實習/實驗\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "Practical Training Lab", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "class participation: 30％\nassignment: 40％\npresentation: 30％", "en": "class participation: 30％\nassignment: 40％\npresentation: 30％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "\"Tue 16-18, Wed 12-16\"", "en": "\"Tue 16-18, Wed 12-16\""}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "資訊管理", "en": "資訊管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "原創性", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉其專業領域文獻", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口